sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>gRPC (HTTP/2)
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS / caikit-nlp<br/>gRPC (HTTP/2)
    participant vLLM as vLLM / OpenAI-compatible<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation with Detection

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>TLS (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC, TLS/mTLS (optional)
    Chunker-->>Orch: Text chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Input detection, TLS/mTLS (optional)
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (input)
    Orch->>TGIS: GenerationService.Generate<br/>gRPC, TLS/mTLS (optional)
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Output detection, TLS/mTLS (optional)
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (output)
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response with detections

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection (OpenAI-compatible)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>TLS (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Token (optional)
    vLLM-->>Orch: Chat completion (SSE stream)
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat<br/>Detection on output, TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: SSE Stream with detections

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>TLS (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk content<br/>gRPC, TLS/mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Text chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content detection, TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Detection Response

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 4: Streaming Content Detection (NDJSON)

    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>NDJSON stream, TLS (optional)
    Orch->>Chunker: Bidirectional streaming chunk<br/>gRPC streaming, TLS/mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Streaming chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Detection per chunk, TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: NDJSON Stream with detections
